			  			I think this may really help people want to stay in the game after they die... even after being full tech<br />
<br />
Here it is, say your full tech and die, when you start new you have to re-research, which NO ONE wants to do...  and im sure most ppl. will wait untill the next set befor playing again, BUT lets say when you restart you get roughly 1/2 of the COMPLETED techs you had when you died...<br />
<br />
I think this will make people stay in the game... dont you?  i know if i died with full tech id wait but if i had 1/2 my researches back when i restarted, i think i would STAY AND REBUILD!!!<br />
<br />
-also i think players (ALL PLAYERS) no matter what, when they start new, even in the beginning new sets, should have - o lets say...   a 24 hour no death time...   cause im sure no one wants to die A S A P.						<P align=right> </P>
